text: Rolf Lauer (11 September 1931 - 25 May 1986) was a German gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics, representing Saar. ==See also== * Saar at the 1952 Summer Olympics ==References== Category:1931 births Category:1986 deaths Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Saar Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Friedrichsthal
